title: Dropbox files for IPO of up to $500M
text:
Dropbox files for IPO of up to $500M Friday, February 23, 2018 - 01:20 
Data-sharing business Dropbox Inc on Friday filed for an initial public offering of up to $500 million with the U.S. Securities and Exchange Commission. ▲ Hide Transcript ▶ View Transcript
